<div class="container">
    <div class="about-section">
        <h2>About PlatePal</h2>
        <p>PlatePal is a comprehensive restaurant review platform designed to help users discover and share dining experiences. Whether you're looking for the best Italian restaurant in town or want to share your thoughts on a hidden gem, PlatePal connects food enthusiasts with quality establishments.</p>
        <p>Our platform features user-generated reviews, owner responses, establishment ratings, and a community-driven approach to making informed dining decisions. With features like favorites, user profiles, and safety moderation tools, PlatePal ensures a safe and enjoyable experience for all users.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="dependencies-section">
        <h2>Technologies & Dependencies</h2>
        <p>This web application is built using Node.js and Express.js framework. Below is a list of all NPM packages and third-party libraries used in the project:</p>

        <h3>Core Dependencies</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>express</strong> (^4.22.1)</li>
            <li><strong>mongoose</strong> (^9.3.0)</li>
            <li><strong>hbs</strong> (^4.2.0)</li>
            <li><strong>bcrypt</strong> (^6.0.0)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Third-Party Libraries</h3>
        <ul>
